                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8694" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0265</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2257 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">驱动可持续发展：百果园的ESG建设之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Driving Sustainable Development:  Pagoda&#39;s ESG Building Journey</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">郑耀洲，于明亮，刘莹，何春艳，崔淼，江诗松</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中南财经政法大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">深圳百果园实业（集团）股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">百果；ESG；可持续发展；企业社会责任；2024百优案例；重点项目；系列4-1</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Pagoda,ESG,Sustainable Development,Corporate Social Responsibility</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，ESG（环境、社会、治理）已成为中国企业可持续发展的“风向标”，它不再是企业的选择题，而是一道必答题。百果园集团，作为中国水果零售行业的领军企业，自2001年成立以来，不仅在业务上实现了跨越式发展，更在ESG建设上展现出其深远的承诺和实践。本案例通过一系列事件描述了根植于百果园中的ESG基因，并重点描述了其在2023年香港交易所成功上市，需要发布ESG报告的契机下，从CSR（企业社会责任）跃迁为ESG的建设之路，即百果园构建ESG组织架构，识别实质性议题，并针对议题梳理行动方向，采取具体举措的实践路径，最终百果园获得了良好的ESG评级。百果园的ESG实践不仅提升了企业形象和市场竞争力，也为行业树立了可持续发展的典范。本案例旨在通过一个真实完整的案例，向学生还原企业ESG建设的全过程，加深学生对ESG相关理论知识点的理解，增强学生ESG与可持续发展的意识，提高学生在环境保护、社会责任和公司治理方面的专业能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In recent years, ESG has become a ‘wind vane’ for the sustainable development of Chinese enterprises, and it is no longer an option for enterprises, but a mandatory question. As a leader in China&#39;s fruit retailing industry, since its establishment in 2001, the Pagoda Group has not only achieved leapfrog development in its business, but has also demonstrated its far-reaching commitment to and practice of environmental, social and governance (ESG). This case describes the ESG genes rooted in Pagoda through a series of events, and focuses on its construction path of leaping from CSR to ESG under the opportunity of its successful listing on the Hong Kong Stock Exchange in 2023 and the need to publish an ESG report, i.e., Pagoda constructed an ESG organisational structure, identified substantive issues, and sorted out the course of action for the issues and took specific initiatives in its practice path, and finally Pagoda obtained a good ESG report. The ESG practice of Pagoda is not only to identify substantive issues, but also to sort out action directions and take concrete initiatives in response to the issues.Pagoda&#39;s ESG practice not only enhances its corporate image and market competitiveness, but also sets a model of sustainable development for the industry. This case study aims to present a real and complete example to students, reconstructing the entire process of corporate ESG development. It deepens students’ understanding of ESG-related theoretical knowledge points, enhances their awareness of ESG and sustainable development, and improves their professional capabilities in environmental protection, social responsibility, and corporate governance.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业伦理》、《ESG与可持续发展》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">（1）核心知识点：ESG概念、ESG驱动因素、ESG体系建设、ESG评级、ESG与公司财务绩效的关系；（2）辅助知识点：可持续发展理论、企业社会责任理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
